high_descs: Go straight and turn towards the sofa on right.

Place the controller on the sidetable.

high_descs: Walk straight ahead to the round table and then turn right to face the sofa on your right.
Pick up the black gaming controller on the couch to the right of the pan.
Turn to your left to face the round table in between the couch and the sidetable.
Set the black gaming controller down on the sidetable on the left side closest to you, below and to the left of the pot in the middle of the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Move the black gaming controller from the couch to the SideTable.
